3. **Explore** - Navigate through all sections using the menu
4. **Customize** - Edit content directly in HTML files (see below)

## 🎨 How to Customize

### Change Messages

**Login message** - Edit in `login.html`:
```html
<p class="subtitle">This space is only for you…</p>
```

**Letter content** - Edit in `js/main.js`:
```javascript
const letterContent = {
    happy: {
        message: 'Your custom message here'
    }
    // ... other letters
}
```

**"Open When" messages** - Edit in `js/main.js`:
```javascript
const openWhenMessages = {
    'cant-sleep': {
        message: 'Your custom message'
    }
    // ... other messages
}
```

**Secret popup message** - Edit in `index.html`:
```html
<p id="secretMessage" class="secret-text">
    Your custom message here
</p>
```

### Add Custom Images

1. Replace SVG drawings in the Drawings section with image tags:
```html
<img src="assets/images/your-image.jpg" alt="Description">
```

2. Or add to the gallery by duplicating a drawing card and changing the image

### Add Music

Replace song links in the Music section (`index.html`):
```html
<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VIDEO_ID" class="song-link" target="_blank">🎧 Listen</a>
```

### Add Background Music

1. Place your audio file in `assets/audio/`
2. Update in `index.html`:
```html
<audio id="bgMusic" loop src="assets/audio/your-song.mp3"></audio>
```

### Change Colors

Edit CSS variables in `styles/main.css`:
```css
:root {
    --dark-green: #1a3d0a;
    --green: #2d5016;
    --light-green: #3d6a1f;
    --soft-green: #7a9d7b;
    --pale-green: #a8c8a9;
    --beige: #f5f5dc;
}
```

## 🔐 Security Notes

- This is a client-side only application (no backend)
- Session storage is used for login (clears when browser closes)
- Change the password in `js/auth.js` if desired
- This is NOT suitable for storing sensitive information
- For a real-world secure site, use proper server-side authentication

